Class TileView

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.board.TileView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TileView
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class to send to the client instead of the real Tile class. It doesn't contain a reference to the player but a player view, that can be safely sent to the client
